summary:
Wooloowoos! Gijinka style!
[Image description: a gif of a digital drawing of a humanised Wooloo from Pokémon, next to its...
body:
Wooloowoos! Gijinka style!

[Image description: a gif of a digital drawing of a humanised Wooloo from Pokémon, next to its Pokémon counterpart, which is a sheep like creature. As a human, she is a dark skinned, chubby girl with off-white hair in two medium-length braids. She is wearing a light brown, sleeveless shirt-dress, a fluffy off-white vest, black tights with hearts on them and light brown boots tied with pink ribbon. She is holding a basket of flowers, and smiling at the viewer in a reclined pose. The flowers in the basket switch between the colours of the lesbian, transgender, bisexual, non binary, pansexual, aromantic and asexual pride flags.]
